'''Hannah Waddingham''' (born 1974) is an English actress. She has appeared in films such as ''Les MisĂŠrables'', ''How to Lose Friends & Alienate People'' and ''The Only Boy for Me'', and TV Shows such as ''Benidorm'', but she is better known in musical theater productions, such as ''A Little Night Music'', ''Into the Woods'', ''The Wizard of Oz'' and ''Spamalot''.

In [[Season 5]] she will portray [[Septa]] [[Unella]], a member of the [[Most Devout]], the ruling council of the [[Faith of the Seven]].<ref>[http://watchersonthewall.com/british-actress-cast-septa-unella/]</ref>
